    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that's a good start. can you go a bit deeper on the sovereignty and rule of law points? my students really need to understand the philosophical/legal foundation behind why some people argue that a country can't function without strict enforcement. like, what's the core logic there?",
